== Wolff Sign-Off

@ Always ON when opener bids 2NT{eq}18-19,
__ #even if an opp has shown a suit# +
@ There are no self-splinters

[%autowidth,cols="^,3*<",grid="none"]
|===
| 1m  |  1M        | |
| 2NT |  ?         | |
|     | !3C!       | | {forces} 3D
|     | !3D!       | | checkback
|     |  3M        | | good suit, or set trump for kickback
|     | 3H (M={S}) | | 5-5 F
|     | 3S (M={H}) | | #*unused*#
|     |  3NT       | | to play
|     |  4C,4D     | | #natural 5-5#
|===

Following checkback and a response, we confirm a fit by bidding the
_other major._

